Class ManagementEntityTypeBuilder.AbstractManagementEntityType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snamp.connectors.ManagementEntityTypeBuilder.AbstractManagementEntityType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ManagementEntityType
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ManagementEntityTypeBuilder.AbstractManagementEntityTabularType, ManagementEntityTypeBuilder.SimpleManagementEntityType
    Enclosing class:
    ManagementEntityTypeBuilder

    public static class ManagementEntityTypeBuilder.AbstractManagementEntityType
extends java.lang.Object
implements ManagementEntityType
    Represents a base class for building custom management entity types.

    You should derive from this class when you want to expose management entity type descriptor as a custom interface that extends ManagementEntityType.

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
